WEBVTT

1
00:00:18.568 --> 00:00:20.887
<b>Today I was at school nice and early</b>

2
00:00:20.887 --> 00:00:23.890
<b>... Which gave me extra time to work on my project</b>

3
00:00:27.944 --> 00:00:29.312
<b>Project...</b>

4
00:00:29.312 --> 00:00:32.315
<b>I am DEFINITELY not doing that today...</b>

5
00:00:32.315 --> 00:00:34.601
<b>Uhh, that will surely happen-</b>

6
00:00:34.934 --> 00:00:37.303
<b>Finn! You're going to be late for school!</b>

7
00:00:37.303 --> 00:00:38.405
<b>Oh, uh</b>

8
00:00:38.405 --> 00:00:39.205
<b>No worries</b>

9
00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:41.141
<b>my Diary says I'll be on time.</b>

10
00:00:57.874 --> 00:00:59.659
<b>This morning was quite exciting, </b>

11
00:00:59.659 --> 00:01:02.662
<b>I only just caught the bus...</b>

12
00:01:03.913 --> 00:01:05.582
<b>How exciting...</b>

13
00:01:06.099 --> 00:01:10.086
<b>[MOTHER] Finn! Does your diary say you'll catch the bus again?</b>

14
00:01:11.404 --> 00:01:14.007
<b>Yes! And only just!</b>

15
00:01:14.424 --> 00:01:15.692
<b>[MOTHER] Hurry up then!</b>

16
00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:28.171
<b>Hey!</b>

17
00:01:28.855 --> 00:01:29.773
<b>Uhh...</b>

18
00:01:29.773 --> 00:01:31.024
<b>Hello?</b>

19
00:01:32.609 --> 00:01:34.577
<b>Do you read that Diary?</b>

20
00:01:34.577 --> 00:01:36.246
<b>Yes, of course!</b>

21
00:01:36.246 --> 00:01:38.198
<b>Why wouldn't I?</b>

22
00:01:38.364 --> 00:01:39.949
<b>Because then it wins, man!</b>

23
00:01:39.949 --> 00:01:42.952
<b>Everything in it seems to be correct because you believe it's correct!</b>

24
00:01:42.952 --> 00:01:45.522
<b>Do you know what happens if you don't read it?</b>

25
00:01:46.356 --> 00:01:48.308
<b>Yeah? Then you know nothing..</b>

26
00:01:48.308 --> 00:01:50.260
<b>Exactly! And that is freedom!</b>

27
00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:52.912
<b>You really don't get what true freedom is, man.</b>

28
00:01:52.912 --> 00:01:54.764
<b>You really have to experience it.</b>

29
00:01:54.764 --> 00:01:55.498
<b>By the way.</b>

30
00:01:55.498 --> 00:01:56.800
<b>Shouldn't you hurry up a bit?</b>

31
00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.301
<b>Your bus is about to leave.</b>

32
00:01:58.301 --> 00:01:59.586
<b>No problem!</b>

33
00:01:59.586 --> 00:02:01.387
<b>According to my Diary I'll catch it just in time anyway.</b>

34
00:02:01.387 --> 00:02:03.056
<b>And, nothing can influence my Diary</b>

35
00:02:03.056 --> 00:02:04.407
<b>So that's just how it is!</b>

36
00:02:04.407 --> 00:02:05.441
<b>You don't know that, huh!</b>

37
00:02:05.441 --> 00:02:07.494
<b>Because, you don't read your diary.</b>

38
00:02:13.149 --> 00:02:15.301
<b>Ouch! There it goes!</b>

39
00:02:15.635 --> 00:02:19.022
<b>But how? My diary is always right!</b>

40
00:02:19.539 --> 00:02:21.057
<b>Heh, that stupid diary.</b>

41
00:02:21.057 --> 00:02:24.410
<b>Everything in it is correct because you believe it's correct</b>

42
00:02:24.594 --> 00:02:26.246
<b>But how?!</b>

43
00:02:26.246 --> 00:02:28.031
<b>Look, I don't read my diary.</b>

44
00:02:28.031 --> 00:02:29.582
<b>That means i am not in the system.</b>

45
00:02:29.582 --> 00:02:31.768
<b>The system, it didn't see me coming!</b>

46
00:02:31.768 --> 00:02:34.771
<b>So that made you slower, and you were late!</b>

47
00:02:35.421 --> 00:02:36.089
<b>What is your name?</b>

48
00:02:36.656 --> 00:02:38.208
<b>Jens, Jens.</b>

49
00:02:38.458 --> 00:02:39.108
<b>Finn</b>

50
00:02:40.043 --> 00:02:41.211
<b>Now I am actually late.</b>

51
00:02:50.386 --> 00:02:54.274
<b>That Jens, he's really not in my Diary!</b>

52
00:02:54.941 --> 00:02:56.426
<b>Did I hear my name there?</b>

53
00:02:56.426 --> 00:02:58.094
<b>You really can't escape me.</b>

54
00:02:58.094 --> 00:02:59.395
<b>And that diary!</b>

55
00:03:00.213 --> 00:03:02.182
<b>And is this conversation in your diary too?</b>

56
00:03:02.182 --> 00:03:04.217
<b>Do you want to escape from the truth?</b>

57
00:03:04.851 --> 00:03:07.203
<b>Everyone is so numbed by that diary</b>

58
00:03:07.203 --> 00:03:10.056
<b>So emotionlessly doing whatever it says.</b>

59
00:03:10.056 --> 00:03:11.374
<b>You know what?</b>

60
00:03:11.374 --> 00:03:13.426
<b>Throw that Diary in that trash can.</b>

61
00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:16.663
<b>What? No! What is wrong with you?</b>

62
00:03:16.663 --> 00:03:19.666
<b>What do you have against a little book that predicts the future?</b>

63
00:03:20.033 --> 00:03:21.284
<b>It doesn't even do that!</b>

64
00:03:21.284 --> 00:03:24.287
<b>Everything in that Diary seems to be correct because you believe it's correct!</b>

65
00:03:24.604 --> 00:03:26.039
<b>So it's bullshit!</b>

66
00:03:27.974 --> 00:03:28.708
<b>Just try it</b>

67
00:03:28.708 --> 00:03:31.711
<b>Try not listening to that Diary like a dog for once.</b>

68
00:03:45.675 --> 00:03:48.661
<b>I got up at 7:00</b>

69
00:03:49.879 --> 00:03:52.882
<b>Like always</b>

70
00:04:09.415 --> 00:04:13.019
<b>Like always, but not today.</b>

71
00:04:22.845 --> 00:04:24.914
<b>Good morning Mom.</b>

72
00:04:24.914 --> 00:04:27.917
<b>Finn! What on earth are you doing here?</b>

73
00:04:27.917 --> 00:04:30.720
<b>You always get out of bed at 7:00, don't you?</b>

74
00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.572
<b>Oh, I thought..</b>

75
00:04:32.572 --> 00:04:35.575
<b>I'm trying something new..</b>

76
00:04:35.575 --> 00:04:37.276
<b>Something new?</b>

77
00:04:37.276 --> 00:04:40.280
<b>But you know what it says in your diary, right?</b>

78
00:04:40.463 --> 00:04:41.597
<b>Yes..</b>

79
00:04:42.815 --> 00:04:44.767
<b>That I would eat peanut butter.</b>

80
00:04:49.288 --> 00:04:51.140
<b>But not today..</b>

81
00:04:59.182 --> 00:05:00.767
<b>Mom...</b>

82
00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:03.770
<b>Today I'm doing things differently..</b>

83
00:05:13.830 --> 00:05:16.833
<b>Look at them, do you see it?</b>

84
00:05:17.016 --> 00:05:17.984
<b>What?</b>

85
00:05:18.151 --> 00:05:22.388
<b>No one looks up, everyone follows their little line from point A to point B.</b>

86
00:05:50.967 --> 00:05:52.969
<b>Why is no one helping?</b>

87
00:05:52.969 --> 00:05:55.655
<b>Because it's not in their script..</b>

88
00:05:55.655 --> 00:05:59.425
<b>16:15, I walk in a straight line towards home</b>

89
00:05:59.859 --> 00:06:04.547
<b>Stopping is a flaw in the system.</b>
<b>Emotion is delay.</b>

90
00:06:05.148 --> 00:06:07.750
<b>What does it say in your little book, Finn?</b>

91
00:06:09.502 --> 00:06:12.872
<b>On the way home I enjoy the quiet</b>

92
00:06:12.872 --> 00:06:14.607
<b>and I think about tomorrow...</b>

93
00:06:14.607 --> 00:06:17.610
<b>Choose. That book. Or your humanity.</b>

94
00:06:26.586 --> 00:06:27.470
<b>Are you okay?</b>

95
00:06:29.972 --> 00:06:31.124
<b>What are you doing?</b>

96
00:06:31.124 --> 00:06:32.558
<b>This, this isn't right!</b>

97
00:06:32.558 --> 00:06:34.343
<b>I'm helping you, you're bleeding!</b>

98
00:07:11.831 --> 00:07:12.498
<b>Finn!</b>

99
00:07:12.498 --> 00:07:14.317
<b>You're forgetting your Diary!</b>

100
00:07:15.468 --> 00:07:16.569
<b>Oh..</b>

101
00:07:17.637 --> 00:07:20.640
<b>I, I don't need it...</b>

102
00:07:35.421 --> 00:07:38.424
<i>Everything in it seems to be correct because you believe it's correct!</i>

103
00:07:40.476 --> 00:07:42.895
<i>I thought freedom was something you were given..</i>

104
00:07:42.895 --> 00:07:44.197
<i>Not something you choose..</i>

105
00:07:46.365 --> 00:07:49.368
<i>Today, I write my own future.</i>

106
00:07:51.487 --> 00:07:52.788
<i>So it's bullshit!</i>
